@0 = ~We're trying to keep civilians off the streets - but you can go wherever you want.~
@1 = ~Thank the gods you're here! Maybe you can save us from these Luskan invaders!~
@2 = ~The entire south section of the city is overrun by the enemy. The city core is the last safe place in Neverwinter... for now.~
